{"tid":2207980,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"騰訊在美遊戲投資，傳引來美國國安審查，已致函Epic Games Inc.、Riot Games等公司","createTime":"2020-09-18T13:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T17:20:08.000Z","uid":109923,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"21641555e98c4c65293edb72fcea166c694f8a52","tid":2207980,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T13:51:20.000Z","msg":"　　中美角力持續升級之際，騰訊 （00700）投資在美遊戲公司，據報引來美國的國家安全審查。騰訊股價今早曾跌逾3%，低見510.5元，現報515元，跌逾2%。<br />\n<br />\n　　彭博引述知情人士透露，特朗普政府要求遊戲公司，提供涉及騰訊控股的數據安全協議的信息。美國外國投資委員會（CFIUS）已致函Epic Games Inc.、Riot Games等公司，詢問其處理美國個人數據的安全協議。<br />\n<br />\n　　其中，騰訊作為全球最大遊戲公司，全資擁有總部位於洛杉磯的Riot Games，並持有開發熱門遊戲《要塞英雄》（Fortnite）的Epic公司4成股份。值得注意，中美關係持續緊張，美國近期加強審查中國公司及其與美國公司的關係。<br />\n<br />\n　　特朗普政府稍早已瞄準中國的字節跳動旗下短片分享平台抖音的海外版TikTok，以及騰訊旗下的WeChat，有關行政令禁止美國居民和公司與TikTok及WeChat做生意，有關限制範圍預計9月20日前後宣布。而TikTok出售美國業務的交易限期，將於20日屆滿。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n騰訊投資外國公司一覽<br />\n<br />\n美國 Riot Games - 100% (4億美元收購)<br />\n香港樂遊科技及其子公司：加拿大Digital Entertainment、英國Splash Damage - 100%(14億美元收購)<br />\n美國 Epic Games - 48.4% (3.3億美元入股)<br />\n韓國 藍洞(Bluehole) / 魁匠團(Krafton) - 11.5% (4.47億美元入股)<br />\n紐西蘭 Grinding Gear Games - 80％<br />\n日本 Marvelous - 20% (5億港元)<br />\n日本 PlatinumGames - 不明<br />\n芬蘭 Supercell - 84.3% (86億美元入股)<br />\n美國 動視暴雪(Activision Blizzard) - 5%<br />\n法國 育碧(Ubisoft) - 5% (3.69億歐元入股)<br />\n荷蘭 Funcom - 29%<br />\n瑞典 Fatshark - 36% (5600萬美元)<br />\n瑞典 Paradox Interactive - 5% (2100萬美元)<br />\n英國 Frontier Developments - 9% (1.77億美元)<br />\n韓國 Netmarble - 17.66%<br />\n韓國 Kakao - 13.5%<br />\n韓國 Eyedentity - 100%<br />\n美國 Discord - 1.58億美元<br />\n美國 Tesla (5%)<br />\n美國 Snapchat (12%)<br />\n美國 Reddit (1.5億美元)<br />\n瑞典 Spotify (10%)<br />\n韓國 Kakao (4.4%)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n失敗收購：<br />\n捷克 BoHemia Interactive - 騰訊有意以2.6億美元收購大多數股權，被拒<br />\n韓國 Nexon &amp; Neople - 騰訊發行60億美元債券融資收購98.64％股份，被拒<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀 - 美國最應該封殺嘅中國企業：騰訊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2141622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2141622</a>"},{"pid":"dd100714cfd0ba5416014a79aa802d0fd288503d","tid":2207980,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:16:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0029f54ea909effbca89572585bb1fcb2f778ce3","tid":2207980,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:17:46.000Z","msg":"遊戲係騰訊金流非常重要的一環<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a524f3642d84ea611de58b1995e2a1cbb7431b","tid":2207980,"uid":36378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:18:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9e4a7cc6c05b2dacd85f11e6c44dec57e5652f","tid":2207980,"uid":212168,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:18:35.000Z","msg":"終於到搞game界   排毒"},{"pid":"d52035411cee2c566d90bb2938be96b46ffff9e7","tid":2207980,"uid":10402,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:09:50.000Z","msg":"快d快d，清晒中國資金打機都安心d"},{"pid":"03500e6305582360807a63ad88d81ced2d3442b6","tid":2207980,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:10:33.000Z","msg":"還我WARFRAME <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19fa5787324e1097399159171b6c0eb05396824","tid":2207980,"uid":58120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:51:29.000Z","msg":"消滅Epic呢個遊戲界公敵仲好"},{"pid":"699db1abc4e6aa00e69071db3e69f2fd5a9dc03a","tid":2207980,"uid":279932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:57:06.000Z","msg":"還我warframe<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gi